<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>This component is assigned to an entity. When the entity changes distance relative to the camera, the <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-render-levelofdetailswitch.xml">LevelOfDetailSwitch</db:link> will disable all the child entities except the one matching index <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-render-levelofdetailswitch.xml#currentIndex-prop">currentIndex</db:link>.</db:para>
